metadata.name: June Bride
metadata.description:
Ajisai(Hydrangea) is a group of small and pretty petals that forms into a one flower that embodies beauty .

Models - Ouka, Nagisa, Natsuki

4200px × 5900px

About"Selfies"
「Fanfare」is an idol group formed by 10 amateurs; they give their best effort every day to be a first-class idols.
Not to mention singing and dancing lessons, but they also
travel around various locations to spread their existence to be known across the world.

For them to be known worldwide,
Fanfare has started an activity to deliver their self-portrait NFT photos called "Selfies" to their fans.

From their private life to how they work, we will deliver a variety of their daily lives.

As a producer, please support your favorite idol.

When NFTs have reached all the fans, the idols will take a new step with you and bring everyone to a "new future."
